          </p>
          <p>
            I am Frills <Speak client:only="react" speak={{ speakText: "Frills", speakPhonetics: "/fr…™lz/" }} />, the proud webmistress of this website in this wondrous wifi world, learn more <Link href={"/about"}>about me</Link> or <Link href={"/colophon"}>about this website</Link>.
          </p>
          <p>Here you will find my latest <Link href={"/blog"}>thoughts</Link> and <Link href={"/experiments"}>experiments</Link>, <a href="/links">portals to other websites</a>, and <Link href={"/guestbook"}>messages</Link> left by other wanderers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <h2 class="visually-hidden">Shrines</h2>
          <a href="/curios/orla" class="gallery" aria-label="Orla (my dog) shrine">
            <img src="/images/curios/orla/orla1.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="" loading="lazy" title="My shrine to Orla!" />
            <img src="/images/curios/orla/orla16.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="" loading="lazy" title="My shrine to Orla!" />
            <img src="/images/curios/orla/orla17.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="" loading="lazy" title="My shrine to Orla!" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
